Detailed Description

Traverses the tasks structure depth first for the average priority of the (direct and indirect) children of some task or tasklist The result can be either retrieved as Priority or Integer, rounded. If all lower level attributedtasks' priorities are unset, Priority.NORMAL is passed back.
